<p>DEFILE</p>
<p>contaminare refers to defilement as the pernicious ruining of what is sound and useful.</p>
<p>inquinare focusses on the sallying or marring of what is inherently beautiful and attractive.</p>
<p>polluere is the desecration of what is spiritually pure or even holy.</p>
